736
00:48:51,245 --> 00:48:52,265
Áno?

737
00:48:52,946 --> 00:48:53,966
Prosím?

738
00:48:55,985 --> 00:48:57,280
Dobre. Hneď tam budeme.

739
00:48:59,626 --> 00:49:02,073
To bolo z obchodu pri byte Ki Eun Young.

